snippet.title: UNDERDOGS PS VR2 Release Date Reveal | VR Games Showcase Spring 2025
snippet.description:
UNDERDOGS is coming to PS VR2 on March 25, with a physical version launching April 4th. Check out exclusive gameplay of the new version, courtesy of One Hamsa and Perp Games!

Wishlist on PS VR2: https://linktr.ee/UnderdogsVRGS
